01:03:41.514 --> 01:03:44.721
Hajde.

01:03:44.754 --> 01:03:48.158
U redu je.

01:03:48.191 --> 01:03:52.162
Pole, u redu je.

01:03:52.194 --> 01:03:56.165
Draga.

01:03:56.198 --> 01:04:00.169
U redu je, srce.

01:04:00.202 --> 01:04:06.209
